<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>My Blog</title>
  <style>
    /* Navigation bar */
    .navbar {
      background-color: #333;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .navbar a {
      float: left;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 17px;
    }

    .navbar a:hover {
      background-color: #ddd;
      color: black;
    }

    /* Blog card */
    .blog-card {
      width: 400px;
      background-color: #f2f2f2;
      border-radius: 5px;
      padding: 10px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .blog-card img {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }

    .blog-card h2 {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .blog-card p {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .blog-card textarea {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100px;
      margin-top: 10px;
      resize: vertical;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="navbar">
    <a href="#">Home</a>
    <a href="#">About</a>
    <a href="#">Contact</a>
  </div>

  <div class="blog-card">
    <h2>Blog Heading</h2>
    <img src="blog-image.jpg" alt="Blog Image">
    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nulla quam lectus, consectetur ac eros a, finibus interdum turpis. Integer vulputate, nisi ac iaculis pulvinar, enim justo volutpat leo, ac posuere nisl mauris ac libero.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
